downloadTitle: Microsoft Dynamics 365 for Field Service Demo Data
downloadDescription: Demo dataset for Microsoft Dynamics 365 for Field Service Demo Data
detailsSection:
To become familiar with Dynamics 365 for Field Service, it’s useful to have a pre-configured environment to explore. For this purpose, we’ve created a separate managed solution that makes it easier to explore and learn about the new solution. Running this package deployer performs the following actions:
• Builds default parameters that drive behavior of field service
• Imports sample data such as resources, roles, work orders and other key information

Important:  There is no way to un-install the demo data. Therefore, you should only use this package on demonstration or test systems.
systemRequirementsSection: Minimum: Microsoft Dynamics 365 fall 2016 release (v8.2) with Field Service (v6.1.0.1462)
installInstructionSection: Download the self-extracting file and extract the contents. Read the "Dynamics 365 for Field Service Demo Data Loader Fall 2016.pdf" file.
